@Chris
One L: The Turbulent True Story of a First Year at Harvard Law School is a 1977 autobiographical book by Scott Turow, and it's pretty well known.

EVOO is a very common shorthand in recipes, and it's what I write on my chalkboard shopping list when I'm running low.

